					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">calima wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Your perception is colored by the NES.</div><br />Actually, my perception is colored by writing programs for regular PCs where a simple division or an array lookup was never really the bottleneck when any of my programs were slow, even on a computer from 1999.<br />But yeah, I don't really know in how far this would be an issue for an emulator.</div>

					
