						<div class="postbody">Bsnes/higan is not only Nestopia but also the Nintendulator of SNES emulators I guess. It's designed to be as hardware accurate as possible. Zsnes is a very old emulator and not very good anymore. It used to be very popular because of its decent compatibility, nice built-in gui and the fact that no highly accurate emulators existed for SNES back then.</div>

